mily:&#39;Times\" new=\"\" roman\';mso-hansi-font-family:\'times=\"\" roman\';\"=\"\">图书馆始终坚持“以人为本、读者第一”的服务宗旨，深入了解通信站官兵的阅读需求，选送图书</span><span style=\"&quot;font-size:15pt;&quot;\" lang=\"&quot;EN-US&quot;\">500</span><span style=\"&quot;font-family:宋体;font-size:15pt;mso-ascii-font-family:&#39;Times\" new=\"\" roman\';mso-hansi-font-family:\'times=\"\" roman\';\"=\"\">余册，期刊</span><span style=\"&quot;font-size:15pt;&quot;\" lang=\"&quot;EN-US&quot;\">230</span><span style=\"&quot;font-family:宋体;font-size:15pt;mso-ascii-font-family:&#39;Times\" new=\"\" roman\';mso-hansi-font-family:\'times=\"\" roman\';\"=\"\">多册，受到通信站官兵的热烈欢迎。图书馆本次送书下基层活动，不仅极大地丰富了通信站官兵的业余文化生活，拓宽和拓展了图书的流通渠道和利用空间，也是结合党的群众路线教育，切实改进工作作风，确保进一步做好读者服务工作的一次重要教育实践活动。</span><span style=\"&quot;font-size:15pt;&quot;\" lang=\"&quot;EN-US&quot;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"&quot;text-indent:29.4pt;margin:0cm\" 0cm=\"\" 0pt;mso-char-indent-count:1.96;\"=\"\" class=\"&quot;MsoNormal&quot;\"><span style=\"&quot;font-size:15pt;&quot;\" lang=\"&quot;EN-US&quot;\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p style=\"&quot;text-indent:29.4pt;margin:0cm\" 0cm=\"\" 0pt;mso-char-indent-count:1.96;\"=\"\" class=\"&quot;MsoNormal&quot;\" align=\"&quot;left&quot;\"><img border=\"&quot;0&quot;\" alt=\"&quot;&quot;\" src=\"images/110229.JPG\"></p> <p style=\"&quot;text-indent:29.4pt;margin:0cm\" 0cm=\"\" 0pt;mso-char-indent-count:1.96;\"=\"\" class=\"&quot;MsoNormal&quot;\"><span style=\"&quot;font-size:15pt;&quot;\" lang=\"&quot;EN-US&quot;\"><o:p></o:p></span>&nbsp;</p><p style=\"&quot;text-indent:29.4pt;margin:0cm\" 0cm=\"\" 0pt;mso-char-indent-count:1.96;\"=\"\" class=\"&quot;MsoNormal&quot;\"><span style=\"&quot;font-size:15pt;&quot;\" lang=\"&quot;EN-US&quot;\"><o:p><img border=\"&quot;0&quot;\" alt=\"&quot;&quot;\" src=\"images/110244.JPG\"></o:p></span></p><p style=\"&quot;text-indent:29.4pt;margin:0cm\" 0cm=\"\" 0pt;mso-char-indent-count:1.96;\"=\"\" class=\"&quot;MsoNormal&quot;\"><span style=\"&quot;font-size:15pt;&quot;\" lang=\"&quot;EN-US&quot;\"><o:p></o:p></span>&nbsp;</p><p style=\"&quot;text-indent:29.4pt;margin:0cm\" 0cm=\"\" 0pt;mso-char-indent-count:1.96;\"=\"\" class=\"&quot;MsoNormal&quot;\"><span style=\"&quot;font-size:15pt;&quot;\" lang=\"&quot;EN-US&quot;\"><o:p><img border=\"&quot;0&quot;\" alt=\"&quot;&quot;\" src=\"images/110256.JPG\"></o:p></span></p><p style=\"&quot;text-indent:29.4pt;margin:0cm\" 0cm=\"\" 0pt;mso-char-indent-count:1.96;\"=\"\" class=\"&quot;MsoNormal&quot;\"><span style=\"&quot;font-size:15pt;&quot;\" lang=\"&quot;EN-US&quot;\"><span style=\"&quot;mso-spacerun:yes;&quot;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></p><p style=\"&quot;text-indent:29.4pt;margin:0cm\" 0cm=\"\" 0pt;mso-char-indent-count:1.96;\"=\"\" class=\"&quot;MsoNormal&quot;\"><span style=\"&quot;font-size:15pt;&quot;\" lang=\"&quot;EN-US&quot;\"><span style=\"&quot;mso-spacerun:yes;&quot;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;文/</span></span><span style=\"&quot;font-family:宋体;font-size:15pt;mso-ascii-font-family:&#39;Times\" new=\"\" roman\';mso-hansi-font-family:\'times=\"\" roman\';\"=\"\">何毅&nbsp; 图/牛宇</span></p>\r\n', '', '0', '0', '', '0', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0', '2016-12-22 10:53:45', '0', '');
